</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Developing and Implementing a Dedicated Prone Positioning Team for Mechanically Ventilated ARDS Patients During the COVID-19 Crisis</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chiu%20M"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Maggie Chiu</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Maggie Chiu</span>, <span class="degrees">PT, DPT, GCS</span>
</h3>
<div>is Physical Therapist, Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, New York-Presbyterian Hospital (NYPH), New York City.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chiu%20M"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Maggie Chiu</span></a>
</div>
</div>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Goldberg%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Adam Goldberg</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Adam Goldberg</span>, <span class="degrees">PT, DPT</span>
</h3>
<div>is Physical Therapist, Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, NYPH.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Goldberg%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Adam Goldberg</span></a>
</div>
</div>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Moses%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Shirah Moses</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Shirah Moses</span>, <span class="degrees">OTR/L</span>
</h3>
<div>Occupational Therapist, Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, NYPH.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Moses%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Shirah Moses</span></a>
</div>
</div>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Scala%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Peter Scala</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Peter Scala</span>, <span class="degrees">PT, MS</span>
</h3>
<div>is Physical Therapist, Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, NYPH.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Scala%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Peter Scala</span></a>
</div>
</div>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fine%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Cynthia Fine</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Cynthia Fine</span>, <span class="degrees">MSN, CRRN</span>
</h3>
<div>is Certified Rehabilitation Registered Nurse, Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, NYPH.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fine%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Cynthia Fine</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>⁎</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ryan%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id6"><span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id6">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span>, <span class="degrees">MA, MS, RN, NP-C, CNS, CWOCN, CCRN</span>
</h3>
<div>is Clinical Nurse Specialist, Adult Care and Intensive Care, Department of Nursing, NYPH. Please address correspondence to Maggie Chiu</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Ryan%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Patrick Ryan</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>⁎</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="anp_a" aria-expanded="false">Article notes</button></li>
